    <string name="help_addon"><![CDATA[An add-on for Suntimes Alarms that dismisses alarms using an NFC tag.]]></string>
    <string name="help_configuration"><![CDATA[<h4>Configuration</h4>
    Open <b>Suntimes Alarms</b> and configure the alarm\'s <b>On Dismiss</b> challenge to <b>Scan NFC Tag</b>.
    <br/><br/>
    Any NFC tag may be used on first use, and that tag will be required for future alarms.
    <br/><br/>
    The NFC tag may be reassigned during an active alarm by scanning another tag at least 5 times.
    <br/><br/>
    The activity runs in configuration mode when started from the launcher; scanning a tag will (re)assign it for future use.
    ]]></string>

